ali Bhagwat]]\n|align=left|[[Shooting at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 10 metre air rifle|10 m air rifle]]\n|393\n|=20\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Shooting at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 50 metre rifle three positions|50 m rifle 3 positions]]\n|575\n|=13\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Deepali Deshpande]]\n|align=left|[[Shooting at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 50 metre rifle three positions|50 m rifle 3 positions]]\n|572\n|19\n|colspan=2|Did not advance\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Suma Shirur]]\n|align=left|[[Shooting at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 10 metre air rifle|10 m air rifle]]\n|396\n|7 '''Q'''\n|497.2\n|8\n|}\n\n==Swimming ==\n{{main|Swimming at the 2004 Summer Olympics}}\n\n;Women\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!colspan=\"2\"|Heat\n!colspan=\"2\"|Semifinal\n!colspan=\"2\"|Final\n|-style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Result\n!Rank\n!Result\n!Rank\n!Result\n!Rank\n|-align=center\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Shikha Tandon]]\n|align=left|[[Swimming at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 50 metre freestyle|50 m freestyle]]\n|27.08\n|40\n|colspan=4|Did not advance\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Swimming at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's 100 metre freestyle|100 m freestyle]]\n|59.70\n|46\n|colspan=4|Did not advance\n|}\n\n==Table tennis==\n{{main|Table tennis at the 2004 Summer Olympics}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!Round 1\n!Round 2\n!Round 3\n!Round 4\n!Quarterfinals\n!Semifinals\n!colspan=2|Final / {{abbr|BM|Bronze medal match}}\n|-style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Opposition<br />Result\n!Rank\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Sharath Kamal]]\n|align=left|[[Table tennis at the 2004 Su