ympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 66 kg|\u221266 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Apostolos Taskoudis|Taskoudis]]|GRE|2004 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133 <sup>{{abbr|PP|Decision by Points - the loser with technical points}}</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Zhirayr Hovhannisyan|Hovhannisyan]]|ARM|2004 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 3\u20131 <sup>{{abbr|PP|Decision by Points - the loser with technical points}}</sup>\n|3\n|colspan=3|Did not advance\n|10\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Sujeet Maan]]\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 74 kg|\u221274 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Kunihiko Obata|Obata]]|JPN|2004 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 0\u20133 <sup>{{abbr|PO|Decision by Points - the loser without technical points}}</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Iv\u00e1n Fundora|Fundora]]|CUB|2004 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 0\u20133 <sup>{{abbr|PO|Decision by Points - the loser without technical points}}</sup>\n|3\n|colspan=3|Did not advance\n|18\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Anuj Kumar]]\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 84 kg|\u221284 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Majid Khodaei|Khodaei]]|IRI|2004 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133 <sup>{{abbr|PP|Decision by Points - the loser with technical points}}</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Hidekazu Yokoyama|Yokoyama]]|JPN|2004 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133 <sup>{{abbr|PP|Decision by Points - the loser with technical points}}</sup>\n|3\n|colspan=3|Did not advance\n|16\n|-align=center\n|align=left|[[Palwinder Singh Cheema]]\n|align=left|[[Wrestling at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's freestyle 120 kg|\u2212120 kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Artur Taymazov|Taymazov]]|UZB|2004 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 0\u20134 <sup>{{abbr|ST|Technical superiority - the loser without technical points by 10-point difference}}</sup>\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Marek Garmulewicz|Garmulewicz]]|POL|2004 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1\u20133 <sup>{{abbr|PP|Decision by Points - the loser with technical points}}</sup>\n|3\n|colspan=3|Did not advance\n|15\n|}\n\